Zserio Java Runtime Library Documentation 1.1.1

Built for Zserio

It implements all functionality needed by Zserio code generated by Java extension.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
zserio.runtime
This package contains helper classes needed for code generated by Zserio.
zserio.runtime.array
This package contains array wrapper which is used for mapping of all zserio arrays.
zserio.runtime.creator
This package contains classes needed for Zserio object creator.
zserio.runtime.io
This package contains stream manipulation classes.
zserio.runtime.json
This package contains classes needed for Zserio JSON debug string.
zserio.runtime.pubsub
This package contains classes for Zserio Pub/Sub.
zserio.runtime.service
This package contains classes for Zserio services.
zserio.runtime.typeinfo
This package contains classes needed for type information generated by Zserio.
zserio.runtime.validation
This package contains classes needed for validation code generated by Zserio.
zserio.runtime.walker
This package contains classes needed for Zserio object walker.

It implements all functionality needed by Zserio code generated by Java extension.

Furthermore, it provides the following convenient functionality for generated Zserio objects which can be called by applications:

  • Serialization (zserio.runtime.io.SerializeUtil.java module)
  • Debug string output (zserio.runtime.DebugStringUtil.java module)

Test coverage report of this library is available as well.
